Map made by Silly                                       June 10 2008

            This is my first map I hope you like it..
      secret room going down the first set of steps at ct spawn on right side shoot wall to the right of the boxes.
      Want to give a shout to DocRock Who helped and inspired me to learn how to make maps.. 
      everyone of his HL1 maps are Top Notch. I would also like to thank Magikus & StarD00d (d00ds.com) for alot of the textures used in this map.
      These guys are the real map makers. My server Noobs Only runs there maps 24/7.
      As far as known issues. The only thing i don't like is the way the bots behave.It's just the design of the map.
      storyline, Terrorist want to destroy a casino in space.  
 
                                    Thanks Silly
